-- Bain May Seek to Enlarge Gome Electrical's Board, China Securities Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-18T00:07:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-18/bain-may-seek-to-enlarge-gome-electrical-s-board-china-securities-reports.html
Bain Capital LLC may seek to enlarge
the board of Gome Electrical Appliances Holdings Ltd., China
Securities Journal reported today, citing Jonathan Zhu Jia, who
represents Bain on Gome’s board.  Zhu confirmed that Gome’s Chairman Chen Xiao, Bain and Gome
founder Huang Guangyu’s family started negotiation this month,
according to the report.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
